<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Fan Page | Balrog</title>
    
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <main>
        <header>
            <img src="Imagens/BalrogPortrait.webp" alt="Retrato do Balrog">
            <h1>Site do Balrog</h1>
            <p>O pugilista mais brutal de Street Fighter</p>
        </header>

        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Pré-luta</h2>
            <p>Aqui vemos Balrog concentrado e estressado antes de entrar no ringue.</p>
            <figure>
                <img src="Imagens/1750932017_large.jpg" alt="Balrog nervoso antes da luta">
                <figcaption>
                    <a href="https://streetfighter.fandom.com/wiki/Balrog" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                        Leia a biografia completa de Balrog
                    </a>
                </figcaption>
            </figure>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Luta Épica</h2>
            <p>Assista a um compilado de momentos incríveis do Balrog em ação.</p>
            <div class="video-wrapper">
                <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/5u_bD2sp7ik?si=FuMuiygOlr_9Ziz_" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Fúria Total!</h2>
            <p>Em sua forma 2D clássica, liberando sua fúria. Não chegue perto!</p>
            <figure>
                <img src="Imagens/SSF2T_Balrog.gif" alt="Balrog em pixel art (GIF animado)">
                <figcaption>Balrog em Super Street Fighter II Turbo</figcaption>
            </figure>
        </section>
    </main>  
</body>
</html>
